accessibility.text: An interactive web site will explain the system and serve as a reference tool for Designers, Product Managers, and Engineers Draft 1 - November 15
Sketch-based UI screen templates, UI components,  colour palettes, type ramps, icons, UX flows, etc.  to accelerate UX design and also maintain consistency. Fogg version live. Draft 1 - December
Support the ability to use design tools (Sketch,  prototyping tools) to create native code/ML  for Bond and Blast. Target: 2017
